org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.expr.xpath
Class AeXPathParseHandler

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.expr.xpath.AeXPathParseHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.jaxen.saxpath.XPathHandler
public class AeXPathParseHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.jaxen.saxpath.XPathHandler

This class listens to a Jaxen parse of an XPath and constructs a list of functions that are used in the expression.
